{
  "texts": [
    "Based on the findings and analyses, recommendations for stakeholders and concluding remarks are provided in Sect. 6.",
    "The experiment was conducted using a York driving simulator, interfaced with a Logitech G27 racing wheel system comprising pedals and a shifter module.",
    "An array of ADAS functions (detailed in Table 1) were assigned to specific buttons on the steering wheel and the shifter module to mimic an authentic driving environment.",
    "The experimental methodology encompassed manoeuvres of an AV in a threedimensional virtual setting.",
    "This vehicle was either autonomous or controlled by the participant, with ADAS functions in either an activated or deactivated state."
  ]
}